1. *Poslednje* što je ona rekla je bilo da će doći sledeće nedelje. (The last thing she said was that she would come next week.)

2. Njegovo *poslednje* delo je bilo previše za njega da završi. (His last work was too much for him to finish.)

3. Ona je počela da se oseća bolje u *poslednjem* trenutku. (She started to feel better in the last moment.)

4. *Poslednje* što je video je bilo neobično. (The last thing he saw was unusual.)

5. Ona je uživala u *poslednjim* dana rada. (She enjoyed her last days working.)